## 5. **README.md**
```markdown
# Event Registration App

A React Native application for event registration with form validation and confirmation screen.

## Features

- üìù User registration form with Name, Email, Phone inputs
- üìÖ Event selection dropdown (Conference, Workshop, Webinar, etc.)
- ‚úÖ Form validation and error handling
- ‚úÖ Confirmation screen with user details
- üé® Beautiful UI with background images and blur effects
- üì± Responsive design for mobile and web

## Screenshots

### Registration Form
![Registration Form](https://via.placeholder.com/300x600/4A90E2/FFFFFF?text=Registration+Form)

### Confirmation Screen
![Confirmation Screen](https://via.placeholder.com/300x600/4CAF50/FFFFFF?text=Confirmation+Screen)

## Technologies Used

- React Native
- React Native Picker
- React Hooks (useState)
- React Native Components (TextInput, TouchableOpacity, etc.)
- Expo

## Installation

1. Clone the repository:
```bash
git clone https://github.com/ewuwise/EventRegistrationApp.git
cd EventRegistrationApp
```

2. Install dependencies:
```bash
npm install
```

3. Run the application:
```bash
npm run web
```

For mobile:
```bash
# iOS
npm run ios

# Android
npm run android
```

## Project Structure

```
EventRegistrationApp/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ App.js               # Main application component
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ RegistrationForm.js  # Registration form component
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Confirmation.js      # Confirmation screen component
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ package.json         # Dependencies and scripts
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ README.md           # This file
```

## Testing IDs

The application includes test IDs for automated testing:

- `formName` - Name input field container
- `formEmail` - Email input field container
- `formPhone` - Phone input field container
- `formPicker` - Event picker container
- `registrationFormDetails` - Registration form container
- `confirmationDetails` - Confirmation screen container
- `confirmText` - Confirmation text
- `registerButton` - Register button
- `backButton` - Back button

## Features in Detail

### Registration Form
- Validates all required fields
- Email format validation
- Phone number validation
- Dropdown event selection
- Error alerts for missing/invalid data

### Confirmation Screen
- Displays user registration details
- Shows success message
- Allows returning to registration form

## License

MIT License
```

